title: 190. Andy & DJ CTI: Antonio Brown, Philly Crime Crisis & DC Protest
itunes:title: 190. Andy & DJ CTI: Antonio Brown, Philly Crime Crisis & DC Protest
description: In today's episode, Andy & DJ discuss the Buccaneers potentially cutting WR Antonio Brown after discovering he wasn't vaccinated, Philadelphia DA Krasner refusing to admit the city has a crime crisis after record homicide numbers, and the protest in DC that shut down traffic in the nation's capital.
